{"tid":2349882,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅比喻過去似「插錯插頭」：2020年係過渡期","createTime":"2021-01-02T01:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T02:23:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"44a6391361d036af3f43033c00003b797b951b2c","tid":2349882,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"《2020年度叱咤樂壇流行榜頒獎典禮》今晚（1/1）舉行，節目期間播出幾位藝人2020年的感悟，其中陳奕迅（Eason）的一番說話卻富有深意，似乎意有所指。<br />\n<br />\n他首先笑稱2020年是個「新紀元」，指過去一年為「過渡期」，更正色道：「全世界都好多人冇嘢做，我覺得係正常嘅，係要抖下。唔係風涼話，唔係話：『梗係啦！你可以afford到個生活！』而係好多嘢要重整。可能好多嘢做緊，我哋係做得錯嘅，即係變咗習慣，但習慣唔代表佢係啱。」<br />\n<br />\n他又比喻過去就似是「插錯插頭」，「即係好多嘢係一路錯緊，原來個插頭係一路插錯咗。不過仲work喎盞燈，咁但係插得唔啱呀嘛！可能有啲嘢要調校。而家呢個世界。我覺得係一個階段接另一個階段嘅中間嗰個交接期。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210101/421793222700830720642795.png/eXy3cdr4gURVw_QBZiQwP_eLvbotkoDCi4eMJ4uHjCc?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210101%2F421793222700830720642795.png%2FeXy3cdr4gURVw_QBZiQwP_eLvbotkoDCi4eMJ4uHjCc%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=33fb60c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a72187581755d4e7cb8a3170f024dfba120f62ee","tid":2349882,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"係咪話走去支那節目做假"},{"pid":"a56fde98f942005e74c4f4bf337e15e9cd562076","tid":2349882,"uid":67208,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T01:48:55.000Z","msg":"講緊trump同拜登交接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反trump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0ff89b71f52ca79eca63640c0b09a3ff1c7dcb